1.Doxygen
- [install] sudo apt-get install doxygen doxygen-gui
- [usage] $ doxywizard

2. DoxigenToolkit.vim (https://vim.sourceforge.io/scripts/script.php?script_id=987)
- [install] 
	1) download DoxygenToolkit.vim from above 
		or
	   use DoxygenToolkit.vim at this directory (note: vim ver.7 needed)
	2) copy the plugin to ~/.vim/plugin
- [usage] (command mode in vim) type ":Dox" when a cursor is on the variable/function's name

3. Doxigen generation script (with pre-defined configuration)
- $./make_doxygen.sh
- run result/html/index.html


